rows.non-certified_products: Diverse Biodynamic® farm with on farm processing & marketing. On 400 acres, we raise 12 acres of vegetables and milk 65 cows. We have a local plus four CSA groups around NYC. Our retail store on the premises is open 7 days a week. We are part of the CRAFT program and offer apprenticeships. We a have a bakery on-site and sell raw milk, yogurt and hard cheeses crafted from our milk.
